Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:52.49,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:01.50,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.32,0:00:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I think I'll tell you a story about a certain Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Persona Black Frost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he lived alone for over thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,While enduring the solitude, he prayed to the sky, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleading, "Give me a friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, the god he served granted him one for a single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the two of them frolicked through the fields, as happy as could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the sun set, his friend vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Frost regretted his request,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for he never would've asked for a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if he had known he would've been left sad and lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence Black Flo—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Flau—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mispronounce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me alter your bodies already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want wrinkles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!{shadow naoto}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been so good to me, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as though we've been friends for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:02:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like just yesterday we entered the TV looking for Naoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That was today, not yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck?! He's getting shaggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a mushroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew! He smells like mold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's changing colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's begin the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see there's another annoying fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna use that attack again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly{senpai}, change Personas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Arahabaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is a fire attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Abaddon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out{senpai}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A lightning attack's coming up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attacks won't connect with her zooming around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to slow her down first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, you're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, you're cool even when you're old!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, you still up and kickin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashter, I shink I'm forgetting shomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hurting these kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I can't fill their bodies with holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was inept at making friends ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after my parents died in an accident and my grandfather took me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I never made any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather would secretly let me help with his client's cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, people started calling me Junior Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that it's come to this, I should fuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I fuse them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we didn't have to get old!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, everyone went nuts over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But my status as a "child" was sufficient to offend many of those whom I worked with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With time, I can become an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything about being a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll never change, even after I grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going to give you a new life as my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I suck at making friends, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Big fuckin' deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate crude simpletons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could be young again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just remem-beared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can bear-come young again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't you have remembered that sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rude to make your elders wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get our youth back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Use Energy Shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-energize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so full of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Beelzebub!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A fly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one huge fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The damage you've inflicted has slowed her down big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna use {\i1}that!{\i0}{it can't be helped}{sugoi powah!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, get running!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing a barrel roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rollin', rollin', rollin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,saw everything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not like being a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you always dress like a boy?{Or maybe naoto x shinji ikari crossover fanfic}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My sex doesn't fit my ideal image of a detective.{Fuck, I ship everyone with shinji}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If they had the slightest "concrete" reason to look down on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,no one would need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know that!{NO! THE GLASS CEILING IS REAL!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that what you yearn for isn't to become an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,or to become a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Try facing yourself.{OMG THAT'S THE SONG NAME!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept ignoring you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending you didn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been inside me.{awww yeaaa}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am you...{made weirder by the fact she keeps saying "boku"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are me.{do any girls in japan actually use boku?}{she's trying to be a dude, faggot. and azusa does in the amagmi ss op}{I hear it a lot in songs, but i'm talking about conversation, bro.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my dream to become a cool, hard-boiled detective someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What I should yearn for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what I must strive for isn't to become a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to accept myself for who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a devious bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you kept something like this hidden for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder the perpetrator has eluded the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, she really put her life on the line for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I never doubted...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'd all come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no genius at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too damn reckless!{he wants to fuck you}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we know.{because he's gay for you}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The case isn't over yet.{but he justifies his gayness since you're actually a girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've proven that to us.{so... episode end? episode end.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, welcome ba—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard? They found Shirogane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, the Detective Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We attend the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He went missing for days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But apparently, they just found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to put a scare into everyone... Yeesh!{>everone... reminds me of this troll someone on rizon tried on gaia http://www.gaiaonline.com/forum/welcome-to-gaia/hai-ever1-im-new-xddddd-p/t.70641627/ didn't exactly work as a troll}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't already know that he'd been found...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You really oughtta do somethin' about that habit of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors spread fast out here, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd he disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he got sulky after being given the boot and ran away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taken off the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I tell you, I was shocked to hear that he up and vanished like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If there had been a fourth kidnapping and murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't have any concrete evidence with that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we gonna make a case like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Dojima's instinct is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe there really is—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I gotta say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit running your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now see here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go study like a normal student...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I killed the mood there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But yeah, I can totally understand why Dojima's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave the case to us police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It would suck if you got caught up in it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are more scary things going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing scary's gonna happen anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, I got the most brains in the whole police department!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was that too hard to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What does "got brains" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It means he's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So things'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, midterms are starting next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bring that up! It's a total buzzkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you fully recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the other day.{She was actually thanking him for the sex}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's with that uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,After some thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to stick with what I've been wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, it's the Detective Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's no prince! He's a she!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda shocked, but also a little disappointed.{girls in background}{i can barely hear this line at all, could easily be nuked imo}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If that's a girl, then holy cow!{overlaps with previous}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, rumors sure spread quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was hoping I could discuss the case with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. We did leave things hanging since the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone lurking in this town is behind all of these kidnappings and murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go into this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(m 658.5 964.5 l 726 1005 796.5 1033.5 897 1056 979.5 1057.5 1035 1054.5 1120.5 1036.5 1188 1008 1252.5 973.5 1294.5 939)}Let's go into this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(m 789 969 l 841.5 985.5 885 996 928.5 1000.5 975 1002 1006.5 1000.5 1045.5 997.5 1126.5 972 1197 937.5)}Let's go into this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My old lady couldn't make this if she tried!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The vichyssoise you made just recently was amazing, too.{http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vichyssoise}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want more! But I don't want to finish it all.{overlaps with previous}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, listen to what Naoto has to say!{overlaps}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were at home when you got kidnapped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It started when my doorbell rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I opened the front door, I saw no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as alarm bells sounded in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,someone grabbed me roughly from behind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and covered my mouth with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately afterward,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was put into something like a sack and carried on someone's shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, how could you remember all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was psychologically prepared for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too damn calm about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by their actions and body type, I'd say the culprit is definitely a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard no conversations or voices,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so I believe he is acting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt a single impact,{my dick is now diamonds}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,which I assume is when I was thrown inside the TV, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But the time from kidnapping to that point seemed too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,About how long did this take?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he caught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it was over in a few minutes.{surprised jukey didn't comment on this line tbh}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So he threw you in the TV right after catching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no question that the culprit is the same in each case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about that Kubo guy who killed Mr. Morooka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a copycat killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the question remains, though, as to how he learned of the world inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's what was bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubo could enter the TV, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't he kill King Moron the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he didn't understand the other world as well as the true culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I can now enter it myself, it wouldn't occur to me to use it for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kubo's criminal act did verify one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer isn't retrieving the bodies and hanging them upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That is simply what happens to the corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,when someone is killed over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So he isn't trying to send some crazy message, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could ask Kubo in person,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,much of our speculation could be tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, if you were so calm, couldn't you have, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean you needed to catch him, but you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,T-To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!{KYUN}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She {\i1}is{\i0} a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, r-right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening to you talk, that totally slipped my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You got balls for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What makes you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A... girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,this case is no longer just a job or someone else's affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to join your effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be reassuring if a famous detective teamed up with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy now, Kanji?{nihihi~}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And ta-da! Here are your glasses, Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, I can sympathize with your drive to find yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to help you in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're a sweetie pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,May I flirt with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't cooperate with you on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, my, my, my, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have a suggestion regarding Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you spend tomorrow after school with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a doctor to take a look at Teddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I thought having a doctor take a look at him might be a good first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So why us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's that fog on the other side, not to mention our powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We should make sure that it isn't negatively affecting our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's results appear normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Teddie? Did you find out anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We certainly did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We learned that we don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had them take an X-ray, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fuzzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had them retake it several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it wise to take that without getting permission first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I intend to return it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,discreetly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't those...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the results to your physical exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too em-bear-rassing if I'm the only one who gets fully exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for some thrilling announcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, if you wanna announce something, start with the girls' three sizes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?! Are you a total moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, is this accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't measure you incorrectly, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?! Which way should I interpret that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool it, perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A-At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the doctors were unable to find any physical problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, we will no longer be needing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Let me take a peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}N-No! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Hanamura! No peeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A-About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait. Were those sizes legit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto's bust size.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But dang, she's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Women fight to be their own selves, even if their secrets get exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,True enough.{TRUE DAT}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching Naoto has taught me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy for me to act tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we went to save Naoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw her accept herself and strive to be true to herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she was pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've decided to be myself and help others understand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're wondering why I shared this with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's because you saved my life, and you're my best bud!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's continue being friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This was in my shoe locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The sender was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She even put down her grade and class number.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Going by the heart seal on the envelope, I doubt this is a commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, there's no reason to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I am only interested in commissions for more cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there is something I would like your help with after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's our rainy day special.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has been able to discern everything that goes in the Mega Beef Bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be a tough case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You always manage to throw me off somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,everything's a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's the case
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,or a beef bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is a series of big events.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath the meat is... more meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And more meat and more meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this based on some sort of set law?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Detective Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A hit-and-run near Samegawa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He just can't get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to keep out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're running away from her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'd go to Heaven if I died?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.89,0:24:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please protect her!
